ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不要分得那麼細<br />\n利申 水上人 真香港人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯 真香港人就係水佬同圍頭佬<br />\n真正本土文化"},{"pid":"73dab8d91c98bd14a633b86866692eb4d2df29df","tid":60281,"uid":33498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台灣人本身就都是大陸移民，罵來罵去有什麼意思。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句真 台狗唔諗下自己咩環境</blockquote><br />\n電騙大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb811fb51b69b311694950d4a727e05fcc29626b","tid":60281,"uid":28338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"香港人根本都係好低質 <br />\n當然比大陸人高d<br />\n但有咩人種衰過大陸人？"},{"pid":"8ce43d6dc11619b29cbec53b92d5aa7496a60096","tid":60281,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人根本都係好低質 <br />\n當然比大陸人高d<br />\n但有咩人種衰過大陸人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n印度巴基斯坦人"},{"pid":"a474213a913a61fa3bf85120f890d873fc0c54d8","tid":60281,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>台灣人本身就都是大陸移民，罵來罵去有什麼意思。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句真 台狗唔諗下自己咩環境</blockquote><br />\n電騙大國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次係香港人柒左<br />\n抹黑人有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}